programme.desc: A group of Song survivors band together to save their prime minister from the encroaching Yuan forces. However, two heroes are imprisoned and must either escape or lose their lives!

programme.title: The Dancing Millionairess
programme.desc: Chen Hou is a chauffeur who gets caught in a mistaken identity scandal linking him to businesswoman Lok Dai. When a rumor gets out that the two are involved in an affair, she's angry and confronts him.

programme.title: The New Shaolin Boxers
programme.desc: An honorable carriage driver finds love and death when he battles particularly venal, homicidal street punks.

programme.title: The Cave Of Silken Web
programme.desc: The 3rd part of Shaw Bros' Journey To The West sees sex and spectacle combine as our heroes are trapped by the seductive 7 Spiders, hellbent on achieving immortality by eating monks!

programme.title: The Wandering Swordsman
programme.desc: An entertaining epic about a hero who robs from the robbers and gives to the poor. Naturally that doesn't make the robbers happy, and they use every sword in the area to try killing their adversary.

programme.title: The Bride From Hell
programme.desc: The 70s idol Hsing Hui and Yon Fan star in this horror movie. Young business man marries pretty, young bride, never knowing that she carries the spirit and everything starts there.

programme.title: The New One-Armed Swordsman
programme.desc: David Chiang leaps into action as all-new one-armed hero when the love of his life is kidnapped and his best friend is murdered by a gang hiding out on Tiger Mountain.

programme.title: A Maid From Heaven
programme.desc: As punishment for bad behaviour, the Jade Emperor's 7th daughter is banished from heaven and sent to live with the humans. There she falls in love with young villager, Dong Young.

programme.title: Shaolin Rescuers
programme.desc: Hong Xi Guan of Shaolin is chased and wounded by a martial arts scum who took refuge in the Qing court. He is saved and healed by friends from the wet market and they hide Hong in a bean curd shop to protect him.

programme.title: Twinkle Twinkle Little Star
programme.desc: A beautiful but ignorant woman is abducted by aliens but nobody believes her close encounter. While planning a suicide to prove herself, she meets a failed detective who is also planning his suicide.

programme.title: Ambush
programme.desc: Ambush sees officer of the law Wan Chao Fan and his father being framed for a robbery they did not commit.

programme.title: Forever Diamonds
programme.desc: Ting Chih-hua, pert and pretty, plans to steal a fabulous diamond ring from a shop. She orders the ring and tells the manager, Tang Chi-tu, to deliver it to psychiatrist Chow Tung-ming.

programme.title: The Three Smiles
programme.desc: A talented scholar, Bo Hu, is attracted by the pretty maid, Qiu Xiang. In order to get close to her and win her love, he disguises as a servant to work in the same household.

programme.title: Hong Kong Nocturne
programme.desc: This film showcases the little seen dancing talents of celebrated kung-fu swordswoman Cheng Pei-Pei, as one of three girls dancing their way to the top.

programme.title: King Cat
programme.desc: The son of the imperial teacher is beheaded by Justice Bao for corruption. Infuriated, the teacher hires assassins to kill Bao, who is saved by Zhan Zhao.

programme.title: Lady General Hua Mu-Lan
programme.desc: This legendary tale of courage and heroism stars Ivy Ling Po as Mulan, the young woman who joined the army and became a true heroine of the Chinese people.

programme.title: The Champion
programme.desc: After years in prison, Lu Hu returns home to find himself set up by his ruthless brother Piao, who has taken over the family coal mine business and imprisoned their sister.

programme.title: The Bride Napping
programme.desc: A rich girl Yue Ying, together with her maid Chun Lan, encounter a poor scholar Bian Ji at a fete. Chun Lan realizes Yue Ying is in love with him, but mixes his identity with a bandit due to an old servant's confusion.

programme.title: Mercenaries From Hong Kong
programme.desc: Filmmaker Wong Jing produced Mercenaries From Hong Kong, his very first modern-day adventure drama. In the dramatic plot he wrote, he sends Ti Lung, Chen Hui-min, Wang Lung-wei, Lo Lieh and Wang Yu on a deadly mission.

programme.title: The Monkey Goes West
programme.desc: Another film inspired by the Chinese classic tale Journey to the West. This memorable version presents a unique interpretation with humour, action, and fantasy galore.

programme.title: The Sword Of Swords
programme.desc: The Sword Master passes on his sword to his disciple Lin before he dies. Another disciple Fang also eyes the sword and plots to take it away from Lin, destroying his family and blinding him in the process.

programme.title: Rose, Be My Love
programme.desc: Not a love triangle but a love rectangle, Rose, be my love is a romantic drama set on the eve of World War II that represents the high standards achieved by Shaw Broathers in both star power and technical polish.

programme.title: King Gambler
programme.desc: A pre-cursor to the gambling craze that swept Asian Cinema, here cardsharp is pitted against cardsharp in a kung-fu fuelled duel of fists and wits to become king of the casino.

programme.title: Double Bliss
programme.desc: Ching Li stars in the story of two students looking to persuade their parents to bless their marriage. The lovebirds hatch what they think is a foolproof plan: they play dead!

programme.title: The Delightful Forest
programme.desc: Imprisoned for murdering his sister-in-law, hero Wu Sung (Ti Lung) meets prison officer Tien Ching and a friendship is formed that may help save the guard's restaurant from thugs.

programme.title: Duel For Gold
programme.desc: Three pairs of cunning male and female crooks trying to steal a million gold taels from the Fu Lai Treasury House.

programme.title: Monkey Kung Fu
programme.desc: Wei Chun is a cocky young man sentenced to jail for killing a man in a fight. One day, Wei Chun picks a fight with an old man that turns out to be the master of monkey style kung fu and as they become friends.

programme.title: Five Tough Guys
programme.desc: The battle between a usurper of the throne and the patriots led by Wu Wen-yuan (Chen Kuan-tai) climaxes to an eventful ending!

programme.title: The Crazy Bumpkins
programme.desc: This side-splitting comedy sees naive Ah Niu (Ya Feng) head to HK, where he is repeatedly exploited and taken advantage of, and eventually finds himself arrested and imprisoned.

programme.title: The Trail Of The Broken Blade
programme.desc: Wang Yu heads a stellar cast in this tale of a swordsman on the run, with his beloved in hot pursuit.

programme.title: The Twin Bracelets

programme.title: Ghosts Galore

programme.title: Disco Bumpkins

programme.title: The Shadow Whip

programme.title: The Blood Brothers

programme.desc: Putri seorang bos triad Hong Kong dituduh membunuh pemimpin saingan mereka. Ia bersembunyi di Korea dan bertemu Ki-chul serta kelompoknya yang ditugaskan untuk melindunginya sampai ia kembali.

programme.title: Ashfall
programme.desc: Saat sebuah gunung berapi yang berada di perbatasan wilayah Tiongkok dan Korea Utara meletus, terjadi gempa bumi yang menyebabkan kekacauan di Korea Utara dan Selatan.

programme.title: The Dude In Me
programme.desc: Seorang siswa SMA terpeleset dari atap sebuah bangunan dan jatuh menimpa seorang mafia. Kemudian di rumah sakit, keduanya bangun dengan tubuh tertukar.

programme.title: An Old Lady
programme.desc: Seorang wanita berusia 69 tahun diperkosa oleh seorang perawat pria yang berusia 29 tahun. Ia memberanikan diri untuk melapor ke polisi, tapi semua orang meragukan kesaksiannya. Mampukah ia melindungi martabatnya?

programme.title: The Odd Family: Zombie On Sale
programme.desc: Keluarga Park yang aneh mencoba mengambil keuntungan dari sebuah eksperimen ilegal perusahaan farmasi yang secara tidak sengaja menciptakan zombie.

programme.title: Confidential Assignment
programme.desc: Kala suatu organisasi kejahatan dari Korea Utara melintasi perbatasan dan memasuki Korea Selatan, seorang detektif Korea Selatan harus bermitra dengan seorang detektif Korea Utara untuk menyelidiki keberadaan mereka.

programme.title: You Are My Sunshine
programme.desc: Kebahagiaan pernikahan Seok-jung dan Eun-ha terancam saat Eun-ha dinyatakan positif HIV dan bertemu kembali dengan mantan suaminya yang kasar.

programme.title: Rolling
programme.desc: Juri yang depresi terjebak di rumah selama penyebaran Covid. Saat ibunya pergi mengunjungi sang nenek, ia harus menjalankan restoran Kimbap sampai ibunya kembali.

programme.title: Along With Gods: Two Worlds
programme.desc: Usai meninggal, pemadam kebakaran Ja-hong dibawa ke alam baka oleh tiga penjaga. Demi bereinkarnasi, ia harus melewati tujuh ujian dalam 49 hari guna membuktikan bahwa ia menjalani kehidupan yang lurus semasa hidup.

programme.title: The Fatal Encounter
programme.desc: Raja Jeongjo diancam oleh faksi Nowon dan Soron yang menjadi lawannya dan berjuang untuk melindungi takhtanya. Ia menghadapi perlawanan dari segala arah dan menjadi target pembunuhan.

programme.title: The Accidental Detective
programme.desc: Seorang penulis blog kriminal dan seorang detektif veteran bekerjasama demi membuktikan bahwa teman mereka tidak bersalah dan dijadikan kambing hitam atas pembunuhan nan keji.

programme.title: Spellbound
programme.desc: Yeo-Ri dapat melihat hantu dan kejadian aneh yang terjadi di sekitarnya. Jo-Goo menawarkan bantuan saat ia bergabung dengan pertunjukan sulapnya sebelum para hantu menjauhkannya dari hidup Yeo-Ri.

programme.title: Oh! My Ghost
programme.desc: Taemin bertemu dengan sosok hantu wanita yang tinggal di studio tempatnya bekerja. Saat sejumlah peristiwa misterius terjadi di studio, mereka bekerja sama untuk menyelidiki dan melindungi studio tersebut.

programme.title: Beasts Clawing At Straws
programme.desc: Didorong oleh rasa putus asa, delapan orang yang bernasib kurang beruntung bertemu dan keadaan menjadi kacau balau saat mereka mengejar tas berisi uang yang misterius.

programme.title: A Werewolf Boy
programme.desc: Seorang gadis remaja nan cantik dikirim ke rumah di pedesaan demi kekayaannya. Ia berteman dengan seorang bocah liar dan mencoba mengajarinya sopan santun, tetapi monster dalam dirinya terus berusaha memberontak.

programme.title: The Book Of Fish
programme.desc: Cendekiawan Joseon Chung Yak-jeon diasingkan selama Persekusi umat Katolik pada tahun 1801. Ia bertemu dengan seorang nelayan dan memutuskan untuk bertukar ilmu pengetahuan dengannya demi menulis buku tentang ikan.

programme.title: Feng Shui
programme.desc: Seorang ahli feng shui tanah, Park Jae-sang, bersaing dengan orang-orang di sekitarnya untuk menempati sebuah lahan keberuntungan demi mengubah nasib mereka dan menjadi seorang raja.

programme.title: Big Match
programme.desc: Seorang pria yang dijebak atas kasus pembunuhan bertarung melawan seorang perancang permainan yang berniat mengubah suatu kota menjadi sebuah permainan raksasa yang dapat ia kendalikan.

programme.title: My Wife Is A Gangster 3
programme.desc: Putri seorang bos triad Hong Kong dituduh membunuh pemimpin saingan mereka. Ia bersembunyi di Korea dan bertemu Ki-chul serta kelompoknya yang ditugaskan untuk melindunginya sampai ia kembali.

programme.title: The Sound Of A Flower
programme.desc: Dalam masyarakat Konfusianisme yang ketat di Korea pada abad ke-19, seorang gadis memutuskan untuk menjadi penyanyi wanita Korea pertama dalam sebuah seni tradisional pansori.

programme.title: The Witch, Pt 2
programme.desc: Seorang gadis misterius yang selamat dari serangan brutal di sebuah laboratorium rahasia mendapati dirinya dilacak oleh sekelompok pembunuh.

programme.title: Papa
programme.desc: Seorang agen pencari bakat asal Korea tiba di Amerika dan melangsungkan pernikahan palsu untuk tinggal di sana. Namun, istrinya meninggal dalam kecelakaan mobil dan meninggalkannya dengan keenam anaknya.

programme.title: Officer Of The Year
programme.desc: Film ini menceritakan tentang persaingan untuk melihat siapa yang melakukan penangkapan terbanyak antara dua polisi ketika mereka dipaksa bekerjasama untuk menangkap seorang penjahat.

programme.title: Always
programme.desc: Usai jatuh cinta dengan seorang telemarketer tunanetra dan menyadari bahwa hal itu karena kesalahannya, seorang mantan petinju memutuskan bertarung dalam pertarungan bawah tanah demi mendapatkan uang untuk operasi.

programme.title: Miss Baek
programme.desc: A woman finds it difficult to shake off her ex-convict label, until she meets a girl whom she is determined to save.

programme.title: Confidential Assignment
programme.desc: When a crime organization from North Korea crosses borders and enters South Korean soil, a South Korean detective must cooperate with a North Korean detective to investigate their whereabouts.

programme.title: Three Sisters
programme.desc: Three sisters reunited for their father's birthday, yet the strange action of their brother reveals their dark past.

programme.title: Spellbound
programme.desc: Yeo-Ri sees ghosts and crazy things happen to the people around her. When she joins Jo-Goo's magic show, he offers to help her find a way out before the ghosts can chase him out of her life.

programme.title: The Dude In Me
programme.desc: In an unfortunate accident, a high school student slips from the roof of a building and falls on top of a mafia. Later in the hospital, the two wake up in each other's bodies.

programme.title: Rolling
programme.desc: Juri with depression is stuck at home during COVID. As her mother went visit Juri's grandmother, Juri has to run their Kimbap restaurant until her mother returns.

programme.title: Beautiful Vampire
programme.desc: A beautiful 500-year-old vampire has her carefully constructed quiet life put in jeopardy when she becomes attracted to her landlady's doltish son.

programme.title: Two Faces Of My Girlfriend
programme.desc: An awkward, almost 30-year-old man meets a sweet, innocent and bashful girl but he soon discovers a completely different side to her!

programme.title: Christmas In August
programme.desc: A teen who owns a photo studio suffers from a fatal disease. He meets a policewoman and falls in love with her. What will be the fate of this love, will it be a tragic ending?

programme.title: The Accidental Detective
programme.desc: A crime-enthusiast blogger and a veteran detective team up to prove the innocence of their mutual friend who's been framed for a horrific murder.

programme.title: Wonderful Ghost
programme.desc: A patrol officer's soul gets separated from his body while he was investigating a case. Unexpectedly he discovers his neighbor who runs a judo studio is the only person can see him.

programme.title: Oh! My Ghost
programme.desc: FD Taemin meets a female ghost who lives in the studio he works. As mysterious events happened in the studio, they join hands to investigate and protect his job and her sleeping place.

programme.title: Along With Gods: Two Worlds
programme.desc: Having died unexpectedly, firefighter Ja-hong is taken to the afterlife by 3 guardians. To reincarnate, he must pass 7 trials in 49 days to prove that he led an upright life while he was still living.
